      "id": "PopularPost196093",
      "post_content": "A little imagination please people. Picture this, a goblin deck, with just a splash of white. Four goblins on the table in front of you, one of them a [Goblin Warchief](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Goblin Warchief), wearing the Crown of Awe upon his pointed green head.\n  \n   \nThen you summon a [Skirk Fire Marshal](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Skirk Fire Marshal), sacrifice the Crown, then tap all five goblins.\n  \n   \nCarnage ensues.\n  \n   \nThis card is indeed...\n  \n   \nAwesome.",
      "posted_by": "Concerned_Bystander",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost196093\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">A little imagination please people.  Picture this, a goblin deck, with just a splash of white.  Four goblins on the table in front of you, one of them a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Goblin Warchief\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Goblin Warchief\">Goblin Warchief</a>, wearing the Crown of Awe upon his pointed green head.\r<br/> <br/>Then you summon a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Skirk Fire Marshal\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Skirk Fire Marshal\">Skirk Fire Marshal</a>, sacrifice the Crown, then tap all five goblins.\r<br/> <br/>Carnage ensues.\r<br/> <br/>This card is indeed...\r<br/> <br/>Awesome.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '196093'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy38571\">Concerned_Bystander</span>\r\n                                (9/16/2011 6:37:27 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00